      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STAYING ALIVE (2) continued her winning form with another strong run to make it two in a row at this track over 300m (16.80). Boasts two wins from three starts out of this box. Great chance again. ZABDON JUSTICE (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (19.42) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. One of the better hopes. MY ERNIE JAY (7) scored (16.61) last time out at this track adding to an already respectable career. Form at the trip excellent including three wins. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. LAKODA FOCUS (8) will be thereabouts after recent top-three finishes.",
